highlights.text: “用背脊唱情歌” by Gareth.T has been on Viral Songs Hong Kong the longest, at 99 days straight.
CORTIS has the most spots on Viral Songs Hong Kong. “GO!” is the highest at #2.
“Yuck (feat. Ken Carson)” by Young Thug and Ken Carson is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Hong Kong, up 22 spots at #57.
“body” by DAYOUNG is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Hong Kong at #1.
